<l>koṭiyār koṭumaiyiṟ ṟāṅkoṭiya vinnā</l>
<l> ṇeṭiya kaḻiyu mirā</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The long nights of these days are far more cruel than the heartless one who is torturing me.</l>
